# Polysnaps — Game Rules for AI

## What is Polysnaps?
An incremental/idle game where you build a network of geometric shapes. Resources flow inward from outer shapes toward a center core shape. Prestige to evolve your core (more sides = more connections = more production).

**Tagline:** Snap. Flow. Grow.

## Core Mechanics
- Center shape collects all resources (starts as triangle, gains sides on prestige)
- Shapes snap to edges of other shapes (free-form, no grid)
- Resources always flow INWARD toward the core
- Each layer of shapes generates for the layer closer to the core
- Fog of war hides the map, expands as you place shapes and upgrade
- Ground has buff zones and puzzle slots
- Shape combos (patterns like stars, big squares) give bonuses
- Permanent shape buffs from events (golden trim, visual + functional)
- Multiple material types unlock with prestige
- Offline idle progression is a must

## Game State
- Game state lives in `src/lib/game/state.svelte.js` using Svelte 5 runes ($state, $derived)
- Game engine tick loop in `src/lib/game/engine.js`
- Save/load via localStorage in `src/lib/game/save.js`
- Offline calculation in `src/lib/game/offline.js`

## Design Doc
Full game design is in `GAME_DESIGN.md` at the repo root. Read it for detailed mechanics.

## Important
- This is an IDLE game — things should produce automatically
- Numbers get BIG — always use formatNumber() from `$lib/utils/format.js`
- Keep the UI clean and readable — retro pixel art style
- The game is a SPA — all on one page, no routing needed beyond the root
